cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with music analysis and generation using machine learning techniques. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper explores relationships between musical elements. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper uses natural language processing techniques (word2vec) to model music. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques to analyze and generate music. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper deals with finding semantically-related slices of music.
